text: Kansas City Royals Dominate the Blue Jays in ALCS Opener 00:46 Edinson Volquez combined with three relievers on a three-hitter and Salvador Perez hit a soaring home run off Toronto starter Marco Estrada.The Blue Jays’ three hits were their fewest ever in a postseason game.Toronto manager John Gibbons said, “Tonight was the Volquez show.
